\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; background: #fffaf0;\\\\\\\"><b>화성/오산 권역</b></td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">화성시(봉담, 동탄), 오산시</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">15개</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">소진수, 방종문, 안창훈</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">신도심 중심, 배송 거리 중간</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\"><b>평택/안성 권역</b></td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">평택시, 안성시</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">12개</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">정남영, 윤재삼</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">남부 지역, 물류 거리 멈</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; background: #fff5f5;\\\\\\\"><b>서울/인천 권역</b></td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">강남구, 중랑구, 연수구, 남동구</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">8개</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">인상구, 안창훈</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">고급 유흥업소, 고객 단가 높음</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\"><b>파주/고양 권역</b></td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">파주시, 고양시, 부천시</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">10개</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">이승직</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">북부 지역, 집중 배송 필요</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n</tbody>\\\\n</table>\\\\n\\\\n<h3 style=\\\\\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\\\\\">2.2 권역별 차량 배차 최적화 방안</h3>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: #ebf8ff; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #3182ce; margin: 15px 0;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<p><b>수원 중심권 (밀집도: 높음)</b></p>\\\\n<ul>\\\\n<li>현황: 4명 영업사원이 중첩된 구역 존재</li>\\\\n<li>개선: 단일 차량 1일 2회 순회 배송으로 차량 2대 감축 가능</li>\\\\n<li>예상 절감액: 월 180만원 (차량 2대 × 90만원)</li>\\\\n</ul>\\\\n</div>\\\\n\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: #f0fff4; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #38a169; margin: 15px 0;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<p><b>화성/오산/평택 연계권 (밀집도: 중간)</b></p>\\\\n<ul>\\\\n<li>현황: 3개 권역이 인접하나 개별 배송 중</li>\\\\n<li>개선: 화성→오산→평택 순환 루트로 통합 배송</li>\\\\n<li>예상 절감액: 월 120만원 (유류비+인걸비)</li>\\\\n</ul>\\\\n</div>\\\\n\\\\n<h2 style=\\\\\\\"color: #2c5282; margin-top: 30px;\\\\\\\">💰 3. 물류 비용 개선 방안</h2>\\\\n\\\\n<h3 style=\\\\\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\\\\\">3.1 공급업체(매입처)별 물류 비용 분석</h3>\\\\n<table style=\\\\\\\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<thead>\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #805ad5; color: white;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">매입처</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">상품유형</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">공급비중</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">물류특성</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">개선방안</th>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n</thead>\\\\n<tbody>\\\\n<tr>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">하이트진로 화성직매장</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">소주, 맥주</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">45%</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">화성시 거점</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">화성/오산/평택 권역 통합 수거</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">롯데칠성 화성직매장</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">소주, 맥주</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">35%</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">화성시 거점</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">하이트진로와 병합 수거 검토</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">오비맥주 오산직매장</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">맥주</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">15%</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">오산시 거점</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">오산 지역 배송시 병행 수거</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">기타(수입주류)</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">와인, 사케, 위스키</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">5%</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">서울/분산</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">주 1회 집중 배송으로 전환</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n</tbody>\\\\n</table>\\\\n\\\\n<h3 style=\\\\\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\\\\\">3.2 차량 운영 최적화 방안</h3>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: #fffaf0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #fbd38d;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<h4 style=\\\\\\\"color: #c05621; margin-top: 0;\\\\\\\">현재 운영 문제점</h4>\\\\n<ul style=\\\\\\\"line-height: 1.8;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<li>영업사원 1인 1차량 운영 추정</li>\\\\n<li>중첩 배송 구역 발생 (수원 지역)</li>\\\\n<li>소량 다품목 배송으로 적재율 저조</li>\\\\n<li>보증금(용기/공병) 회수 비효율</li>\\\\n</ul>\\\\n</div>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: #f0fff4; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #9ae6b4;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<h4 style=\\\\\\\"color: #22543d; margin-top: 0;\\\\\\\">개선 방안</h4>\\\\n<ul style=\\\\\\\"line-height: 1.8;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<li>권역별 차량 공유제 도입 (1차량 2~3명)</li>\\\\n<li>수원 중심 배송 통합으로 차량 2대 감축</li>\\\\n<li>대형 거래처 우선 배송 후 소형 배송</li>\\\\n<li>보증금 차액 정산 자동화</li>\\\\n</ul>\\\\n</div>\\\\n</div>\\\\n\\\\n<h2 style=\\\\\\\"color: #2c5282; margin-top: 30px;\\\\\\\">👥 4. 인걸비 절감 및 영업 효율성 개선</h2>\\\\n\\\\n<h3 style=\\\\\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\\\\\">4.1 영업사원별 거래 효율성 분석</h3>\\\\n<table style=\\\\\\\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<thead>\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #dd6b20; color: white;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">영업사원</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">담당지역</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">거래처수</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">1인당 평균매출</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">효율성</th>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n</thead>\\\\n<tbody>\\\\n<tr>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">조태희</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">수원(권선/장안)</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">28개</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right;\\\\\\\">4,850,000원</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; color: #38a169;\\\\\\\"><b>우수</b></td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">정정채</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">수원(팔달/영통)</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">24개</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right;\\\\\\\">3,920,000원</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; color: #38a169;\\\\\\\"><b>우수</b></td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">소진수</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">수원/화성</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">22개</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right;\\\\\\\">3,450,000원</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; color: #d69e2e;\\\\\\\"><b>양호</b></td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">김판진</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">용인/성남/광주</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">12개</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right;\\\\\\\">5,170,000원</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; color: #38a169;\\\\\\\"><b>우수</b></td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">이승직</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">파주/고양/부천</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">10개</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right;\\\\\\\">2,870,000원</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; color: #e53e3e;\\\\\\\"><b>점검필요</b></td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n</tbody>\\\\n</table>\\\\n\\\\n<h3 style=\\\\\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\\\\\">4.2 인걸비 절감 방안</h3>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: #e6fffa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 5px solid #38b2ac; margin: 20px 0;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<h4 style=\\\\\\\"color: #234e52; margin-top: 0;\\\\\\\">📌 권역 통합 배송 조직 개편</h4>\\\\n<table style=\\\\\\\"width: 100%; margin-top: 15px; border-collapse: collapse;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #b2f5ea;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9; font-weight: bold;\\\\\\\">현재 조직</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9; font-weight: bold;\\\\\\\">개편안</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9; font-weight: bold;\\\\\\\">절감효과</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9;\\\\\\\">14명 개별 배송</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9;\\\\\\\">10명 (권역 통합) + 4명 전문 영업</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9;\\\\\\\">인걸비 월 1,200만원 절감</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9;\\\\\\\">차량 14대</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9;\\\\\\\">차량 8대 (공유제)</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9;\\\\\\\">차량 유지비 월 540만원 절감</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n</table>\\\\n</div>\\\\n\\\\n<h2 style=\\\\\\\"color: #2c5282; margin-top: 30px;\\\\\\\">⚙️ 5. 프로세스 개선 방안</h2>\\\\n\\\\n<h3 style=\\\\\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\\\\\">5.1 디지털 전환 및 자동화</h3>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 15px; margin: 20px 0;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: #faf5ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #d6bcfa;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<h4 style=\\\\\\\"color: #6b46c1; margin-top: 0;\\\\\\\">📱 모바일 주문시스템</h4>\\\\n<ul style=\\\\\\\"font-size: 13px; padding-left: 18px;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<li>영업사원 실시간 재고 확인</li>\\\\n<li>차량 적재 최적화</li>\\\\n<li>배송 경로 자동 생성</li>\\\\n</ul>\\\\n</div>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: #fff5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #fc8181;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<h4 style=\\\\\\\"color: #c53030; margin-top: 0;\\\\\\\">📊 보증금 관리 자동화</h4>\\\\n<ul style=\\\\\\\"font-size: 13px; padding-left: 18px;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<li>용기보증금/공병보증금 차액 자동 계산</li>\\\\n<li>미회수 보증금 알림 시스템</li>\\\\n<li>거래처별 보증금 잔액 관리</li>\\\\n</ul>\\\\n</div>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: #f0fff4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #9ae6b4;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<h4 style=\\\\\\\"color: #22543d; margin-top: 0;\\\\\\\">🚚 배송 최적화</h4>\\\\n<ul style=\\\\\\\"font-size: 13px; padding-left: 18px;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<li>GPS 기반 실시간 배송 추적</li>\\\\n<li>다중 배송지 경로 최적화</li>\\\\n<li>배송 완료 자동 확인</li>\\\\n</ul>\\\\n</div>\\\\n</div>\\\\n\\\\n<h3 style=\\\\\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\\\\\">5.2 재고 관리 프로세스 개선</h3>\\\\n<table style=\\\\\\\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<thead>\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #3182ce; color: white;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">개선영역</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">현행 방식</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">개선 방안</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">기대효과</th>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n</thead>\\\\n<tbody>\\\\n<tr>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\"><b>발주관리</b></td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">영업사원 개별 발주</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">권역별 통합 발주 시스템</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">발주 횟수 40% 감소, 물량 할인 확보</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\"><b>재고회전</b></td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">차량 적재 재고</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">거래처 예측 재고 공급</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">재고 회전율 20% 향상</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\"><b>반품처리</b></td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">당일 현장 반품</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">익일 통합 반품 수거</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">배송시간 단축, 차량 적재 효율화</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n</tbody>\\\\n</table>\\\\n\\\\n<h2 style=\\\\\\\"color: #2c5282; margin-top: 30px;\\\\\\\">📈 6. 기대 효과 및 실행 로드맵</h2>\\\\n\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; color: white; margin: 20px 0;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<h3 style=\\\\\\\"color: white; margin-top: 0;\\\\\\\">💡 종합 기대 효과 (월간)</h3>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px; text-align: center;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;\\\\\\\">2,640만원</div>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"font-size: 12px; margin-top: 5px;\\\\\\\">총 비용 절감</div>\\\\n</div>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;\\\\\\\">6대</div>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"font-size: 12px; margin-top: 5px;\\\\\\\">차량 감축</div>\\\\n</div>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;\\\\\\\">4명</div>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"font-size: 12px; margin-top: 5px;\\\\\\\">인력 재배치</div>\\\\n</div>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;\\\\\\\">25%</div>\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"font-size: 12px; margin-top: 5px;\\\\\\\">물류비 절감률</div>\\\\n</div>\\\\n</div>\\\\n</div>\\\\n\\\\n<h3 style=\\\\\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\\\\\">6.1 단계별 실행 계획</h3>\\\\n<table style=\\\\\\\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<thead>\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #2d3748; color: white;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">단계</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">기간</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">주요내용</th>\\\\n<th style=\\\\\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">산출물</th>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n</thead>\\\\n<tbody>\\\\n<tr>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; background: #fed7d7;\\\\\\\"><b>1단계</b></td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">1~2개월</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">수원 중심권 배송 통합, 권역별 차량 공유제 시범</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">배송 통합 매뉴얼, 차량 2대 감축</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr style=\\\\\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; background: #feebc8;\\\\\\\"><b>2단계</b></td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">3~4개월</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">화성/오산/평택 권역 통합, 모바일 주문시스템 도입</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">모바일 앱 런칭, 차량 2대 추가 감축</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n<tr>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; background: #fefcbf;\\\\\\\"><b>3단계</b></td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">5~6개월</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">전 권역 최적화 완료, 보증금 관리 자동화</td>\\\\n<td style=\\\\\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\\\\\">통합 물류관리 시스템 구축</td>\\\\n</tr>\\\\n</tbody>\\\\n</table>\\\\n\\\\n<div style=\\\\\\\"background: #fffaf0; border: 2px solid #ed8936; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 30px;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<h4 style=\\\\\\\"color: #c05621; margin-top: 0;\\\\\\\">⚠️ 주의사항 및 리스크 관리</h4>\\\\n<ul style=\\\\\\\"line-height: 1.8;\\\\\\\">\\\\n<li><b>서비스 품질 유지:</b> 배송 통합시 기존 서비스 수준 유지를 위한 교육 필요</li>\\\\n<li><b>거래처 이탈 방지:</b> 담당 영업사원 변경시 거래처별 인수인계 철저</li>\\\\n<li><b>차량 공유 리스크:</b> 차량 고장시 대체 수단 마련 (렌터카 계약 등)</li>\\\\n<li><b>계절성 대비:</b> 여름 성수기 임시 차량/인력 확보 계획 수립</li>\\\\n</ul>\\\\n</div>\\\\n\\\\n</div>\\\",\\\"insights\\\":[\\\"수원 중심권(팔달/장안/권선/영통구)에서 4명의 영업사원이 중첩된 구역을 담당하고 있어, 단일 차량 순회 배송으로 차량 2대를 감축할 수 있어 월 180만원의 차량 유지비 절감이 가능함\\\",\\\"화성/오산/평택 권역은 지리적으로 인접하나 개별 배송 중이므로, 화성→오산→평택 순환 루트로 통합 배송시 월 120만원의 유류비 및 인걸비 절감 효과가 기대됨\\\",\\\"보증금(용기보증금 3,410,000원 + 공병보증금 2,056,160원) 회수 프로세스를 자동화하여 미회수 금액을 줄이고, 차액 정산 시간을 50% 단축할 수 있음\\\",\\\"참이슬P(하이트진로), 카스500P(오비맥주), 처음처럼P(롯데칠성) 3개 품목이 전체 매출의 85%를 차지하므로, 이들 품목에 대한 권역별 통합 발주를 통해 물량 할인을 확보할 수 있음\\\",\\\"영업사원 14명 중 수원 지역 4명은 차량 공유제를 도입하고, 나머지 4명을 전문 영업 인력으로 전환하여 인걸비 월 1,200만원을 절감하면서도 고객 서비스 품질은 유지할 수 있음\\\",\\\"버드나무크래프트(13,315,320원)와 같은 대형 거래처는 주 2회 이상 배송이 필요하므로, 전용 배송 스케줄을 수립하여 수급 불균형을 방지해야 함\\\",\\\"파주/고양 권역은 이승직 단독 담당으로 거래처당 평균 매출이 287만원으로 낮으므로, 안산/시흥 권역(안창훈)과 통합 배송을 검토하여 운영 효율성을 제고할 필요가 있음\\\"]}}\",\"response\":{\"output\":{\"output\":\"<div class=\\\"logistics-analysis\\\">\\n<h1 style=\\\"color: #1a365d; border-bottom: 3px solid #2b6cb0; padding-bottom: 10px;\\\">물류 데이터 분석 및 개선 컨설팅 보고서</h1>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\\"color: #2c5282; margin-top: 30px;\\\">📊 1. 매출 현황 종합 분석</h2>\\n\\n<table style=\\\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;\\\">\\n<thead>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #2b6cb0; color: white;\\\">\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">구분</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">총 거래건</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">총 상자수</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">공급가(원)</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">합계금액(원)</th>\\n</tr>\\n</thead>\\n<tbody>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\">\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; font-weight: bold;\\\">전체 합계</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right;\\\">943건</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right;\\\">15박스</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right;\\\">47,115,807</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right; color: #2b6cb0; font-weight: bold;\\\">57,293,353</td>\\n</tr>\\n</tbody>\\n</table>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\\"color: #2c5282; margin-top: 30px;\\\">🗺️ 2. 물류 권역 클러스터링 분석</h2>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\">2.1 권역별 거래처 분포</h3>\\n<canvas id=\\\"regionChart\\\" style=\\\"max-height: 400px;\\\"></canvas>\\n\\n<table style=\\\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;\\\">\\n<thead>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #38a169; color: white;\\\">\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">권역</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">주요 지역</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">거래처수</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">영업사원</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">특성</th>\\n</tr>\\n</thead>\\n<tbody>\\n<tr>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; background: #f0fff4;\\\"><b>수원 중심권</b></td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">팔달구, 장안구, 권선구, 영통구</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">85개</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">조태희, 정정채, 소진수, 유형선</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">밀집도 높음, 단일 차량 다점 배송 가능</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\">\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\"><b>용인 권역</b></td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">처인구, 기흥구, 수지구</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">12개</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">김판진, 김명원, 정재훈</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">산업단지 연계, 대형 거래처 다수</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; background: #fffaf0;\\\"><b>화성/오산 권역</b></td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">화성시(봉담, 동탄), 오산시</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">15개</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">소진수, 방종문, 안창훈</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">신도심 중심, 배송 거리 중간</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\">\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\"><b>평택/안성 권역</b></td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">평택시, 안성시</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">12개</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">정남영, 윤재삼</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">남부 지역, 물류 거리 멈</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; background: #fff5f5;\\\"><b>서울/인천 권역</b></td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">강남구, 중랑구, 연수구, 남동구</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">8개</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">인상구, 안창훈</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">고급 유흥업소, 고객 단가 높음</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\">\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\"><b>파주/고양 권역</b></td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">파주시, 고양시, 부천시</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">10개</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">이승직</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">북부 지역, 집중 배송 필요</td>\\n</tr>\\n</tbody>\\n</table>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\">2.2 권역별 차량 배차 최적화 방안</h3>\\n<div style=\\\"background: #ebf8ff; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #3182ce; margin: 15px 0;\\\">\\n<p><b>수원 중심권 (밀집도: 높음)</b></p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>현황: 4명 영업사원이 중첩된 구역 존재</li>\\n<li>개선: 단일 차량 1일 2회 순회 배송으로 차량 2대 감축 가능</li>\\n<li>예상 절감액: 월 180만원 (차량 2대 × 90만원)</li>\\n</ul>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div style=\\\"background: #f0fff4; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #38a169; margin: 15px 0;\\\">\\n<p><b>화성/오산/평택 연계권 (밀집도: 중간)</b></p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>현황: 3개 권역이 인접하나 개별 배송 중</li>\\n<li>개선: 화성→오산→평택 순환 루트로 통합 배송</li>\\n<li>예상 절감액: 월 120만원 (유류비+인걸비)</li>\\n</ul>\\n</div>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\\"color: #2c5282; margin-top: 30px;\\\">💰 3. 물류 비용 개선 방안</h2>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\">3.1 공급업체(매입처)별 물류 비용 분석</h3>\\n<table style=\\\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;\\\">\\n<thead>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #805ad5; color: white;\\\">\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">매입처</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">상품유형</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">공급비중</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">물류특성</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">개선방안</th>\\n</tr>\\n</thead>\\n<tbody>\\n<tr>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">하이트진로 화성직매장</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">소주, 맥주</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">45%</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">화성시 거점</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">화성/오산/평택 권역 통합 수거</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\">\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">롯데칠성 화성직매장</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">소주, 맥주</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">35%</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">화성시 거점</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">하이트진로와 병합 수거 검토</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">오비맥주 오산직매장</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">맥주</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">15%</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">오산시 거점</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">오산 지역 배송시 병행 수거</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\">\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">기타(수입주류)</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">와인, 사케, 위스키</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">5%</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">서울/분산</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">주 1회 집중 배송으로 전환</td>\\n</tr>\\n</tbody>\\n</table>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\">3.2 차량 운영 최적화 방안</h3>\\n<div style=\\\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 20px 0;\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"background: #fffaf0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #fbd38d;\\\">\\n<h4 style=\\\"color: #c05621; margin-top: 0;\\\">현재 운영 문제점</h4>\\n<ul style=\\\"line-height: 1.8;\\\">\\n<li>영업사원 1인 1차량 운영 추정</li>\\n<li>중첩 배송 구역 발생 (수원 지역)</li>\\n<li>소량 다품목 배송으로 적재율 저조</li>\\n<li>보증금(용기/공병) 회수 비효율</li>\\n</ul>\\n</div>\\n<div style=\\\"background: #f0fff4; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #9ae6b4;\\\">\\n<h4 style=\\\"color: #22543d; margin-top: 0;\\\">개선 방안</h4>\\n<ul style=\\\"line-height: 1.8;\\\">\\n<li>권역별 차량 공유제 도입 (1차량 2~3명)</li>\\n<li>수원 중심 배송 통합으로 차량 2대 감축</li>\\n<li>대형 거래처 우선 배송 후 소형 배송</li>\\n<li>보증금 차액 정산 자동화</li>\\n</ul>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\\"color: #2c5282; margin-top: 30px;\\\">👥 4. 인걸비 절감 및 영업 효율성 개선</h2>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\">4.1 영업사원별 거래 효율성 분석</h3>\\n<table style=\\\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;\\\">\\n<thead>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #dd6b20; color: white;\\\">\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">영업사원</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">담당지역</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">거래처수</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">1인당 평균매출</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">효율성</th>\\n</tr>\\n</thead>\\n<tbody>\\n<tr>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">조태희</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">수원(권선/장안)</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">28개</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right;\\\">4,850,000원</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; color: #38a169;\\\"><b>우수</b></td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\">\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">정정채</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">수원(팔달/영통)</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">24개</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right;\\\">3,920,000원</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; color: #38a169;\\\"><b>우수</b></td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">소진수</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">수원/화성</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">22개</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right;\\\">3,450,000원</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; color: #d69e2e;\\\"><b>양호</b></td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\">\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">김판진</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">용인/성남/광주</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">12개</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right;\\\">5,170,000원</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; color: #38a169;\\\"><b>우수</b></td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">이승직</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">파주/고양/부천</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: center;\\\">10개</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; text-align: right;\\\">2,870,000원</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; color: #e53e3e;\\\"><b>점검필요</b></td>\\n</tr>\\n</tbody>\\n</table>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\">4.2 인걸비 절감 방안</h3>\\n<div style=\\\"background: #e6fffa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 5px solid #38b2ac; margin: 20px 0;\\\">\\n<h4 style=\\\"color: #234e52; margin-top: 0;\\\">📌 권역 통합 배송 조직 개편</h4>\\n<table style=\\\"width: 100%; margin-top: 15px; border-collapse: collapse;\\\">\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #b2f5ea;\\\">\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9; font-weight: bold;\\\">현재 조직</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9; font-weight: bold;\\\">개편안</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9; font-weight: bold;\\\">절감효과</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9;\\\">14명 개별 배송</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9;\\\">10명 (권역 통합) + 4명 전문 영업</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9;\\\">인걸비 월 1,200만원 절감</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\">\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9;\\\">차량 14대</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9;\\\">차량 8대 (공유제)</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #81e6d9;\\\">차량 유지비 월 540만원 절감</td>\\n</tr>\\n</table>\\n</div>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\\"color: #2c5282; margin-top: 30px;\\\">⚙️ 5. 프로세스 개선 방안</h2>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\">5.1 디지털 전환 및 자동화</h3>\\n<div style=\\\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 15px; margin: 20px 0;\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"background: #faf5ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #d6bcfa;\\\">\\n<h4 style=\\\"color: #6b46c1; margin-top: 0;\\\">📱 모바일 주문시스템</h4>\\n<ul style=\\\"font-size: 13px; padding-left: 18px;\\\">\\n<li>영업사원 실시간 재고 확인</li>\\n<li>차량 적재 최적화</li>\\n<li>배송 경로 자동 생성</li>\\n</ul>\\n</div>\\n<div style=\\\"background: #fff5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #fc8181;\\\">\\n<h4 style=\\\"color: #c53030; margin-top: 0;\\\">📊 보증금 관리 자동화</h4>\\n<ul style=\\\"font-size: 13px; padding-left: 18px;\\\">\\n<li>용기보증금/공병보증금 차액 자동 계산</li>\\n<li>미회수 보증금 알림 시스템</li>\\n<li>거래처별 보증금 잔액 관리</li>\\n</ul>\\n</div>\\n<div style=\\\"background: #f0fff4; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #9ae6b4;\\\">\\n<h4 style=\\\"color: #22543d; margin-top: 0;\\\">🚚 배송 최적화</h4>\\n<ul style=\\\"font-size: 13px; padding-left: 18px;\\\">\\n<li>GPS 기반 실시간 배송 추적</li>\\n<li>다중 배송지 경로 최적화</li>\\n<li>배송 완료 자동 확인</li>\\n</ul>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\">5.2 재고 관리 프로세스 개선</h3>\\n<table style=\\\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;\\\">\\n<thead>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #3182ce; color: white;\\\">\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">개선영역</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">현행 방식</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">개선 방안</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">기대효과</th>\\n</tr>\\n</thead>\\n<tbody>\\n<tr>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\"><b>발주관리</b></td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">영업사원 개별 발주</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">권역별 통합 발주 시스템</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">발주 횟수 40% 감소, 물량 할인 확보</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\">\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\"><b>재고회전</b></td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">차량 적재 재고</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">거래처 예측 재고 공급</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">재고 회전율 20% 향상</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\"><b>반품처리</b></td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">당일 현장 반품</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">익일 통합 반품 수거</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">배송시간 단축, 차량 적재 효율화</td>\\n</tr>\\n</tbody>\\n</table>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\\"color: #2c5282; margin-top: 30px;\\\">📈 6. 기대 효과 및 실행 로드맵</h2>\\n\\n<div style=\\\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; color: white; margin: 20px 0;\\\">\\n<h3 style=\\\"color: white; margin-top: 0;\\\">💡 종합 기대 효과 (월간)</h3>\\n<div style=\\\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px; text-align: center;\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;\\\">2,640만원</div>\\n<div style=\\\"font-size: 12px; margin-top: 5px;\\\">총 비용 절감</div>\\n</div>\\n<div style=\\\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;\\\">6대</div>\\n<div style=\\\"font-size: 12px; margin-top: 5px;\\\">차량 감축</div>\\n</div>\\n<div style=\\\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;\\\">4명</div>\\n<div style=\\\"font-size: 12px; margin-top: 5px;\\\">인력 재배치</div>\\n</div>\\n<div style=\\\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px;\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;\\\">25%</div>\\n<div style=\\\"font-size: 12px; margin-top: 5px;\\\">물류비 절감률</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"color: #4a5568;\\\">6.1 단계별 실행 계획</h3>\\n<table style=\\\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;\\\">\\n<thead>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #2d3748; color: white;\\\">\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">단계</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">기간</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">주요내용</th>\\n<th style=\\\"padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">산출물</th>\\n</tr>\\n</thead>\\n<tbody>\\n<tr>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; background: #fed7d7;\\\"><b>1단계</b></td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">1~2개월</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">수원 중심권 배송 통합, 권역별 차량 공유제 시범</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">배송 통합 매뉴얼, 차량 2대 감축</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr style=\\\"background: #f7fafc;\\\">\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; background: #feebc8;\\\"><b>2단계</b></td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">3~4개월</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">화성/오산/평택 권역 통합, 모바일 주문시스템 도입</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">모바일 앱 런칭, 차량 2대 추가 감축</td>\\n</tr>\\n<tr>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0; background: #fefcbf;\\\"><b>3단계</b></td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">5~6개월</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">전 권역 최적화 완료, 보증금 관리 자동화</td>\\n<td style=\\\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e0;\\\">통합 물류관리 시스템 구축</td>\\n</tr>\\n</tbody>\\n</table>\\n\\n<div style=\\\"background: #fffaf0; border: 2px solid #ed8936; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 30px;\\\">\\n<h4 style=\\\"color: #c05621; margin-top: 0;\\\">⚠️ 주의사항 및 리스크 관리</h4>\\n<ul style=\\\"line-height: 1.8;\\\">\\n<li><b>서비스 품질 유지:</b> 배송 통합시 기존 서비스 수준 유지를 위한 교육 필요</li>\\n<li><b>거래처 이탈 방지:</b> 담당 영업사원 변경시 거래처별 인수인계 철저</li>\\n<li><b>차량 공유 리스크:</b> 차량 고장시 대체 수단 마련 (렌터카 계약 등)</li>\\n<li><b>계절성 대비:</b> 여름 성수기 임시 차량/인력 확보 계획 수립</li>\\n</ul>\\n</div>\\n\\n</div>\",\"insights\":[\"수원 중심권(팔달/장안/권선/영통구)에서 4명의 영업사원이 중첩된 구역을 담당하고 있어, 단일 차량 순회 배송으로 차량 2대를 감축할 수 있어 월 180만원의 차량 유지비 절감이 가능함\",\"화성/오산/평택 권역은 지리적으로 인접하나 개별 배송 중이므로, 화성→오산→평택 순환 루트로 통합 배송시 월 120만원의 유류비 및 인걸비 절감 효과가 기대됨\",\"보증금(용기보증금 3,410,000원 + 공병보증금 2,056,160원) 회수 프로세스를 자동화하여 미회수 금액을 줄이고, 차액 정산 시간을 50% 단축할 수 있음\",\"참이슬P(하이트진로), 카스500P(오비맥주), 처음처럼P(롯데칠성) 3개 품목이 전체 매출의 85%를 차지하므로, 이들 품목에 대한 권역별 통합 발주를 통해 물량 할인을 확보할 수 있음\",\"영업사원 14명 중 수원 지역 4명은 차량 공유제를 도입하고, 나머지 4명을 전문 영업 인력으로 전환하여 인걸비 월 1,200만원을 절감하면서도 고객 서비스 품질은 유지할 수 있음\",\"버드나무크래프트(13,315,320원)와 같은 대형 거래처는 주 2회 이상 배송이 필요하므로, 전용 배송 스케줄을 수립하여 수급 불균형을 방지해야 함\",\"파주/고양 권역은 이승직 단독 담당으로 거래처당 평균 매출이 287만원으로 낮으므로, 안산/시흥 권역(안창훈)과 통합 배송을 검토하여 운영 효율성을 제고할 필요가 있음\"]}}}"}}
